textBeforeTable: Title: “These Fluid Moments” This clip is from a DVD called “These Fluid Moments”. Late August scenes from North Stradbroke Island show how a comfortable wetsuit can enhance your surfing opportunities. Music by a local composer from the band Salt Lickin' Hicks.     www.facebook.com/howlingplanetphotography DVD rrp AUS$20 info@howlingplanet.com   SIZING GUIDE - PLEASE FOLLOW THE MANUFACTURER'S GUIDELINES.     HOTSKINS are designed to be worn under a wetsuit to increase warmth or with boardshorts to reduce wind chill.   The TITANIUM lining reflects heat back to the body, keeping your body warmer and in the water longer.   HOTSKIN vests are made of high-tech neoprene that combines the flexibility of a neoprene with the warmth normally associated with bulky jackets.   0.5mm SHORT SLEEVE
